        {
            "title": "爆一爆｜咩世代？一張公仔卡等於160斤黃金（Louise）",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_BRL37.Xn7BZ1vI74UqkMg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/9821bf40-19cb-11f1-a662-1002ed37076d\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">赤馬紅羊之年，中東瞬間炮彈滿天飛，金、股、滙及油價都大上大落。恒指都企唔穩26000點。不過有隻細價股係大跌浪成為逆市奇萉，真係講都唔信又唔識，話說將Pokémon卡變成基金推出，間公司迷策略（2440.HK）股價，三日就升咗45%，呢啲就係GEN Z 新世代投資產品。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link rapid-with-clickid etailiffa-link athena-button\" data-i13n=\"sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Yahoo;elmt:other;pdid:\" data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Yahoo;elmt:other;pdid:;itc:0\" href=\"https://yfinance.onelink.me/3068494570?pid=editorial&amp;c=HK_Acquisition_YMktg_Evergreen_[…]ub2=HK_YMktg&amp;af_sub3=&amp;af_sub4=1058&amp;af_sub5=article__Banner_\" rel=\"sponsored\" target=\"_blank\">下載Yahoo財經APP</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇</strong></p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">老餅去追金 Gen Z就追卡</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">去年11月底金價突破$4000美元一盎司時，引發老餅一族去追金買銀，當時參觀一個名為 Grade10 Festival 嘅活動，睇吓啲Gen Z新世代投資啲乜，驚嘆老餅去追金，Gen Z就追卡。睇到啲本地及內地新世代，喺合和酒店會場內人頭湧湧，除來自各地嘅交易平台卡商、原來有鑑證公司幫啲卡主做鑑證，股票分藍籌及細價股，卡都有唔同嘅級數，10分為最高評級，咪好似標普同穆迪咁嘅評級機構，真係有啲金融市場運作嘅雛型。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6592e5d4-e749-4b70-b007-68bc7e488819-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><blockquote class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull\" style=\"padding-bottom:min(300px, undefined%)\"></div></blockquote><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">過年前，有張極罕有嘅PSA10 評級的《比卡超插畫家》Pikachu Illustrator Pokémon 卡，以$1.28億港元成交；嘩，輕飄飄一張卡等於160斤黃金（以每兩$5萬港元計），任你托都未必托得走，呢啲真係新世代嘅另類投資。而全球Pokémon 卡價亦水漲船高，升值妣媄黃金。搞到紐約有Pokémon 店遇劫，香港亦發生Pokémon 卡盜竊案，真係做差佬都要與時並進了解失竊物品何解咁值錢。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">迷策略老細 曾做過財經主播</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">個Grade10 Festival 搞手就你迷策略老細陳展程（Ray），佢四十出頭， 由搞爛GAG文化變身為上市公司主席都算傳奇。讀Law出身嘅佢，除咗做過月入不夠＄1萬嘅Now財經台主播之外，其實喺永隆銀行做過Legal Compliance，呢啲銀行經驗同佢現時檔生意都息息相關。試問揸住幾條黃金，都要揾保險箱收埋先得。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">迷策略乘勢鑽到個揾錢位，推出「Grade10 保管庫」幫啲卡主做埋認證，如果有卡主揸住 Pokémon 卡升值到百萬、千萬，保管庫又係商機噃。用埋佢 Solana區塊鏈，經實體資產(RWA)代幣化系統，幫卡主鑄張「Twin Digital 」。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"迷策略老細陳展程（左二）早前親身見證《比卡超插畫家》以$1.28億港元成交。\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"454\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/X8aN_eb4U.J0FRLwxS.L4A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUzOQ--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/0fcb4ac0-19cc-11f1-be78-e757d44d0965\" width=\"809\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:809px\">迷策略老細陳展程（左二）早前親身見證《比卡超插畫家》以$1.28億港元成交。</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">唔單止保管庫，仲出埋基金產品。 就在迷策略宣佈推出全球首隻 Pokémon 藏卡代幣化基金，股價就彈起。基金投資於市值＄9400萬美元「梵高比卡超卡牌」PSA10，基金會同數字平台EVIDENT合作，係市場掃入25%呢類型嘅卡。不過係俾「專業投資者」認購，小妹自認專業，但銀行戶口未達專業水平咯，未夠班落叠。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">香港成日自認係文化之都，估唔到一張「比加超」嘅藏卡都可以玩到出神入化。以前有人講「有錢就有文化」，今日要改口啦，「有文化就有錢」。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%88%86%E4%B8%80%E7%88%86%EF%BD%9C%E5%92%A9%E4%B8%96%E4%BB%A3%EF%BC%9F%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%B5%E5%85%AC%E4%BB%94%E5%8D%A1%E7%AD%89%E6%96%BC160%E6%96%A4%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%EF%BC%88louise%EF%BC%89-022149310.html",
